# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# cookies.txt — OPTIONAL, only needed for heavy load testing
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# For light usage (~2 req/h), yt-dlp works fine without cookies.
#
# If running load tests, export cookies from your browser in
# Netscape format and save to api/cookies.txt, then either:
#   - Rebuild the Docker image, or
#   - Mount the file at runtime:
#       docker run -v $(pwd)/api/cookies.txt:/app/cookies.txt ...
#
# How to export:
#   - Browser extension: "Get cookies.txt" (Netscape format)
#   - yt-dlp: yt-dlp --cookies-from-browser chrome
#                --cookies cookies.txt
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
